  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636270/extras/6ce7c13c5dd129778bb2b2cfe2da2149.avif?t=1644768345\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Dragons once roamed the skies. Now they are only old tales.<br><br>Visual/Kinetic Novel about love, sacrifice, family, and loneliness with a bit different approach to the concept of dragons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this story you will:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> live with three half-dragon girls<br></li><li> meet with the Queen-Empress<br></li><li> get thrown in a jail<br></li><li> hope you won't get killed</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (Depends on your reading speed).",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636270/extras/6ce7c13c5dd129778bb2b2cfe2da2149.avif?t=1644768345\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Dragons once roamed the skies. Now they are only old tales.<br><br>Visual/Kinetic Novel about love, sacrifice, family, and loneliness with a bit different approach to the concept of dragons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this story you will:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> live with three half-dragon girls<br></li><li> meet with the Queen-Empress<br></li><li> get thrown in a jail<br></li><li> hope you won't get killed</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (Depends on your reading speed).",
